window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dive back into the sexy side of the Upper East Side with the second billionaire romance from <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author K. A. Linde.&nbsp;</p> <p>I finally have everything I ever wanted - fame and fortune and literary success.&nbsp;</p> <p>Only one problem: I lost my muse.&nbsp;</p> <p>He was tall, dark, and handsome. Broody, enigmatic, alluring, and right for me in every way.&nbsp;</p> <p>Until he wasn't. Until I lost everything.&nbsp;</p> <p>And I can't lose it all again. I'll do anything to keep it.&nbsp;</p> <p>Even seeing him again....</p> <p><i>Contains mature themes.</i></p>"; 
